{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://wwfalcon.github.io/sdc_toolkits_page/","title":"PSD SDC Toolkits","description":"PSD SDC Toolkits."}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"产品策略：为你的产品构建策略愿景","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"产品策略：为你的产品构建策略愿景","meta_description":"产品策略描绘了产品最终的愿景，产品的终止之地。通过构建产品策略，你可以决定产品的努力方向。","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":null,"toc":null,"keywords":["产品策略","策略愿景","步骤","策略要素"]},"html":"<p>来源：</p>\n<p><a href=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/concepts/product-strategy-setting-your-strategic-vision-for-product-offerings_zh_CN\">Product strategy: Setting your strategic vision for product offerings,MaRS Library</a></p>\n<p>产品策略描绘了产品最终的愿景，产品的终止之地。通过构建产品策略，你可以决定产品的努力方向。</p>\n<p>类似于地图的有效使用方式，你需要首先明确一个目的地，然后规划你的行进路线。当业务具备了一个策略愿景，描述了当业务成长后，它要成为何物，产品也就具备了它的策略及目标。</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/static/31f274961254a46fbe738ef900371057/8cd40/product-strategy-2_20180601.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 62.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"product-strategy-2_20180601\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/static/31f274961254a46fbe738ef900371057/8cd40/product-strategy-2_20180601.png\"\n        srcset=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/static/31f274961254a46fbe738ef900371057/e90f4/product-strategy-2_20180601.png 163w,\n/sdc_toolkits_page/static/31f274961254a46fbe738ef900371057/da05d/product-strategy-2_20180601.png 325w,\n/sdc_toolkits_page/static/31f274961254a46fbe738ef900371057/8cd40/product-strategy-2_20180601.png 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h2 id=\"产品策略为何重要\"><a href=\"#%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>产品策略为何重要?</h2>\n<p>产品策略是<a href=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/concepts/intro-to-product-roadmaps-date-based-theme-based-and-technology_zh_CN\">产品路线图</a>，以及后续的<a href=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/concepts/determining-the-product-release_zh_CN\">产品释放</a>的执行基础。</p>\n<h2 id=\"产品策略要素\"><a href=\"#%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>产品策略要素</h2>\n<p>当定义产品策略时，要明确已回答了如下问题。</p>\n<p>注意：如下每个问题对应的链接都会指向一个更广泛的主题，要确保在制定策略之前已阅读了这些主题。</p>\n<h3 id=\"要卖给谁\"><a href=\"#%E8%A6%81%E5%8D%96%E7%BB%99%E8%B0%81\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/concepts/Who_are_you_selling_to_zh_CN\">要卖给谁?</a></h3>\n<p>定义目标客户或市场，明确要卖给谁，目标市场是什么。</p>\n<h3 id=\"卖的是什么\"><a href=\"#%E5%8D%96%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/concepts/What_are_you_selling_zh_CN\">卖的是什么?</a></h3>\n<p>要向潜在客户阐述你的产品和其它竞争性产品的区别，要让他们理解是什么保证了你的产品在市场上的唯一性。</p>\n<h3 id=\"为客户提供哪些价值\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/concepts/What_value_do_you_provide_your_customers_zh_CN\">为客户提供哪些价值?</a></h3>\n<p>要明确你的产品要为客户解决什么问题。在一个特定的市场里，你不能让你的产品面面俱到，但你可以设法解决某些特定的问题。为客户提供的解决方案要定位于提供特定的价值。</p>\n<h3 id=\"产品如何定价\"><a href=\"#%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%B7\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/concepts/your-tech-product-pricing-and-product-positioning-in-the-marketing-mix_zh_CN\">产品如何定价?</a></h3>\n<p>声明你的产品如何计价，包括它的可识别价值及价格模型。</p>\n<h3 id=\"产品如何分发\"><a href=\"#%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%88%86%E5%8F%91\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/concepts/How_will_you_distribute_your_product_zh_CN\">产品如何分发?</a></h3>\n<p>描述产品如何销售，目标市场如何获取到你的产品。</p>\n<h2 id=\"创建产品策略\"><a href=\"#%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>创建产品策略</h2>\n<p>要创建产品策略，首先要明确你要解决的<a href=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/concepts/identifying-market-problems_zh_CN\">市场问题</a> ，包括要针对目标市场做用户<a href=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/concepts/interviewing-potential-users_zh_CN\">访谈</a>,理解市场的全面竞争态势，并区分出你的产品特殊性。</p>\n<p>当你对市场理解的更为深入，或者你要进入到不同的市场，你的产品策略有可能会随之变更。倾听市场的声音，随之调整市场策略会是一个反复的过程，当你理解更为深入后，你的市场策略会进化到解决更多的问题。</p>\n<h2 id=\"示例：产品策略\"><a href=\"#%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>示例：产品策略</h2>\n<p>以下是一个产品策略的简要描述示例，你的产品策略会有所不同，内容可能会更多，但要体现之前描述的要素。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>我们为住宅中的厨房用户提供高质量的炊具</li>\n<li>我们的客户是年轻一代北美用户，他们需要炊具能经受住孩子的摔打，炊具的材质要对儿童是安全的，并且要环保</li>\n<li>我们通过零售渠道销售产品</li>\n<li>我们的产品按单件定价，价格要定位到高端区间</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"产品策略的力量\"><a href=\"#%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>产品策略的力量</h2>\n<p><strong>产品策略的力量来自于清晰的定义：哪些能做，哪些不能做</strong> 。在产品策略中，要明确目标市场，也要明确排除某些其他市场，这样才会使公司理解不符合产品策略的哪些项目会失败，并且会导致策略目标分心。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>总结</h2>\n<p>产品策略勾勒了一个公司的策略轮廓，产品向何处去，如何抵达目的地以及为何会成功抵达。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"后续阅读\"><a href=\"#%E5%90%8E%E7%BB%AD%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>后续阅读</h2>\n<p><a href=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/concepts/strategic-planning-product-differentiation-strategy-and-market-type_zh_CN\">策略规划：依据市场类型制定不同的产品差异化策略</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"参考资料\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>参考资料</h2>\n<p>McGrath, M. E. (2001). <em>Product Strategy for High Technology Companies</em>. New York: McGraw-Hill.</p>\n<p>Thomson, B. (2004). <em>Creating a Strategic Product Plan</em>. Retrieved June 30, 2010, from <a href=\"/sdc_toolkits_page/concepts/http:/pragmaticmarketing.com/resources/creating-a-strategic-product-plan\">http://www.pragmaticmarketing.com/publications/topics/08/how-to-make-product-management-strategic</a></p>","fields":{"slug":"/concepts/product-strategy-setting-your-strategic-vision-for-product-offerings_zh_CN/"},"timeToRead":3,"excerpt":"来源： Product strategy: Setting your strategic vision for product offerings,MaRS Library…","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/gavinwang/Documents/Working/codes/sdc_toolkits/content/concepts/product-strategy-setting-your-strategic-vision-for-product-offerings_zh_CN.md"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/concepts/product-strategy-setting-your-strategic-vision-for-product-offerings_zh_CN/"}}